{"type": "article", "id": 24826, "title": "箪笥拉杆箱", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-01T06:54:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607165659VY8LIRwJTmbdFjqa.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个木质的拉杆箱来自日本设计团队yuukou yamaguchi ，他们结合了日本传统家具箪笥的特征，将它做成抽屉形式。每个抽屉都使用了“inome”图案，在抽屉的正中间配上了金属拉环，很古典。箱子的大小符合了行李箱规定的大小，有收缩的推拉杆和滚轮，并将重量控制在 10 千克里，但它更像是方便移动的小型储物柜。<br></p>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607165656oUY2MrE7Gk1zQB95.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607165657bM1EKV6okvHXDRAu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75183374\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607165657YyfjgKMV6wBAZsF0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607165658XBdA6mWrReYpuk3q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607165658hljcnqVE3T9ZO5bJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66870416\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}